# AI Resume Builder — Agent Instructions

## First Step Every Session

1. Read `PROJECT_MEMORY.md` at the project root for full context
2. After completing work, update `PROJECT_MEMORY.md` changelog and status tables

## Conventions

- Bilingual: all user-facing strings go in `src/lib/i18n/translations.ts`
- Arabic locale uses RTL (`dir="rtl"` on html)
- API keys only in `.env.local`, never committed
- ATS prompts live in API route files under `src/app/api/`
- Resume templates are React components in `src/components/resume/templates/`
- Use existing UI components from `src/components/ui/`

## Do Not

- Commit `.env.local` or API keys
- Break RTL layout for Arabic
- Add resume templates without updating PROJECT_MEMORY.md template table
